unittitle_ssm: Teamsters for a Democratic Union, New York - New Jersey Chapter Records
abstract_ssm: Teamsters for a Democratic Union was formed in the 1970s by rank-and-file members of the International Brotherhood of Teamsters to combat corruption in their union.  The New York - New Jersey regional office of the TDU was established in 1987.  Materials include administrative records of the TDU, materials related to the International Brotherhood of Teamsters, records pertaining to Teamsters locals, records related to divisions within the union, individual grievances, legal records, correspondence, resource materials, and photographs.
